steps.name: Given I navigate to the DemoBlaze home page
Navigate to DemoBlaze home page
$("open") https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html
$("webdriver") create()
Given I add "Samsung galaxy s6" to cart
Add product Samsung galaxy s6 to cart
$(".card-title[0]") click()
$("By.linkText: Add to cart") click()
$("open") https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html
And I add "Nokia lumia 1520" to cart
